$interpreted: Naya: Angel, even if you're busy, there should be a limit to how much you work. It's Christmas today; you should take a proper rest.
Angelia: I'll take a break after I finished the work I have here. Naya, you can take a break first.
Naya: In the past, during this time of the year, the castle would host a huge party. In contrast, it's so quiet and... uneventful this year. Can't get used to this.
Angelia: As long as everyone is living safely and peacefully in this world, I will be very satisfied...
Angelia: A party is too much of a luxury at this point. I can't ask for more...
Guard: Hey! Who are you? How dare you trespass into the Royal residence!
Angelia: Tica!?

Tica: Princess~~ Long time no see~
I'm here to deliver Christmas presents!
Guard: You should leave, NOW!
Angelia: It's alright. She is someone I know.

Naya: Tica, why are you wearing that outfit?
Didn't you go back to Rune Academy?

Tica: Tehee~ I'm not Tica today!
Today, I'm the Christmas girl that brings everyone joy and fun!!
Tica: This is my present for you girls~~
Dagger: STOP RIGHT THERE~~~!!
Angelia: Sir Dagger? Why are you here as well?

Dagger: Finally caught up to you!
Hand me the presents you are holding, now!

Tica: Aww~ Didn't I give you one already?
If you want another one, there's still plenty of them here~
Dagger: Give me all of them, every single one.
Tica: Eheheh? These... these don't seem like the presents I originally planned to deliver?
Dagger: That's because you grabbed the wrong bag to begin with! Those are MY presents!
Naya: There's some writing on the box. An... I think it says "Angel" !?
Naya: Looks like it's a present for you?
Angelia: A present from Sir Dagger? For me?
Dagger: No... I mean, don't open it!
Angelia: This cookie smells really nice.
Naya: That Bear knows how to bake cookies?!
Dagger: Tha... That's not a cookie... Give it back!
Angelia: It's delicious.
Naya: Angel...
Angelia: What's wrong?
Naya: Nothing; it's just that you seem kind of depressed for the past few days. It's good to see you smile again.
Angelia: The cookies really are delicious. Naya, you should try it.
Naya: Holy, you're not kidding! This is really tasty! I would pay good money for this! Dagger, did you make these yourself?
Dagger: Is... is it really that tasty?

Angelia: One of the best cookies I've ever eaten.
Sir Dagger, you really are amazing.
Dagger: Good to hear you like it!
Kittyeyes: Present thief! Give me back my present!
Roger: How dare you steal my sister's present! I will not let you off the hook easily!
Koll: Arooooo!
Sherlock: That's the one! He's the one who snatched my present!
Lisa: Father, stop acting like a man-child! It's so embarrassing~ Come on, let's go back...
Ned: Lisa, we should help Sir Sherlock get back his present first.
Izumi: Hehe, I've always wanted to say this line too~
Izumi: Show me the present!!!
Angelia: Nigel?
Nigel: Angel? What is going on here?
Yamitsuki: ......
Hestia: Give the things back.
Yan-Bo: Better than riches, a good name is. Forgiveness, we will grant.
Pang: If you refuse to return what you've stolen, forgive me for resorting to force.

Tica: Woah~ Didn't expect everyone to be here.
No need to rush; there are enough presents for everybody~~
Tica: Are you ready? Three~ Two~ One~

Tica: We wish everyone in the world,
MERRY CHRISTMAS!!~
Angelia: What a pretty Christmas present~
Kittyeyes: Hey, you big dumb bear! Gimme back my present.
Dagger: What present?
Kittyeyes: Don't try to play dumb!
Hestia: Hey! Stop pushing!
Sherlock: Wait, I can't get over there!
Lisa: Father... See, I knew this is going to happen! That's why I told you not to come!
Izumi: Haha, pushing around one another is a lot of fun too!
Roger: Don't you dare hurt Kittyeyes!
Dagger: She the one who attacked me first though...
Naya: Yep, we need a party after all.
Angelia: You're right. This is how Christmas should be, with everyone together having all the fun we can~
？？？: Unforgivable... Unforgivable...
？？？: If I don't get a present, then nobody gets one...
